# Assets Insurance Deferred Reinsurance Expense Policies Future Accounting Amount

## identifier
de8311

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of deferred reinsurance expense that relates to future business not yet written, determined in accordance with prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Insurance.DeferredReinsuranceExpensePoliciesFutureAccounting.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.09
- period=instant
